{"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Run scripts automatically when a VM boots."}],"kind":"article","topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/diskInject","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/ssh","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/agent","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/sharedFolder","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/VirtualMachineSpecification","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/VirtualMachineBundle"],"anchor":"Provisioning-Modes","title":"Provisioning Modes"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/spooktacularkit\/provisioning"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"macOS virtual machines don’t have a cloud-init equivalent. Spooktacular","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provides provisioning modes to bridge this gap. Today, SSH provisioning","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"is fully working. Disk-inject is in progress, and two more modes (guest","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"agent and shared-folder watcher) are planned.","type":"text"}]},{"level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Choosing a Mode","anchor":"Choosing-a-Mode"},{"type":"table","header":"row","rows":[[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Mode"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Status"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Works without setup?"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Network needed?"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Best for"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/ssh","type":"reference","isActive":true}]}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Working","type":"text"}]}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Need SSH enabled","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Yes","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Cloned VMs with SSH","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/diskInject","type":"reference"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In progress"}],"type":"strong"}]}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Yes","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"No"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Fresh IPSW installs, CI runners","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/agent"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Planned","type":"text"}]}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Need agent installed"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"No","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"OCI images (future)","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/ProvisioningMode\/sharedFolder","type":"reference","isActive":true}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Planned"}]}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Need watcher","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"No","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"No-disk-modify environments"}]}]]]},{"level":3,"type":"heading","text":"SSH (Working)","anchor":"SSH-Working"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"After boot, Spooktacular discovers the VM’s IP, connects via SSH,","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"and executes your script. You get real-time output streaming.","type":"text"}]},{"code":["spook start my-vm \\","    --user-data ~\/setup.sh \\","    --provision ssh \\","    --ssh-user admin"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"bash"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Requires:","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" Remote Login enabled in the guest","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"(System Settings -> General -> Sharing -> Remote Login).","type":"text"}]},{"level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Disk Inject (In Progress)","anchor":"Disk-Inject-In-Progress"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Before the VM boots, Spooktacular mounts the guest’s data volume","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and writes a standard macOS LaunchDaemon that executes your script.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This is the only mode that will work on a completely vanilla macOS","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"install. This mode is currently being implemented.","type":"text"}]},{"code":["spook create my-vm --from-ipsw latest \\","    --user-data ~\/setup.sh \\","    --provision disk-inject"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"bash"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Guest Agent (Planned)","anchor":"Guest-Agent-Planned"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The Spooktacular guest agent will communicate over VirtIO socket — a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"direct host-guest channel that works without networking. This mode","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"is planned for a future release.","type":"text"}]},{"level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Shared Folder (Planned)","anchor":"Shared-Folder-Planned"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The script will be delivered via a VirtIO shared folder. A watcher","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"daemon in the guest will execute new scripts automatically. This","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"mode is planned for a future release.","type":"text"}]}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/Provisioning","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit"],["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/CLIReference"],["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/EC2MacDeployment"],["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/GettingStarted"],["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/GitHubActionsGuide"],["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/KubernetesGuide"],["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/MLWorkloads"],["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/RemoteDesktop"],["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/BlueBubblesGuide","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/GettingStarted"],["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/BlueBubblesGuide","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/RemoteDesktop"],["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/docu